u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 $138,800.00<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n6.0pt;margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.75in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>The\nestimated span time to perform the services note above: 17 days<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n6.0pt;margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.75in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>Lead\ntime: 15 days for paint procurement<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n6.0pt;margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:0in;margin-right:22.5pt;\nmargin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:27.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-27.0pt'><b><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>2.0</span></b><b><span\nstyle='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><b><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>Pricing\nDetail:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>2.1\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Strip and paint fuselage and vertical stabilizer.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.25in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>2.2\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Scuff sand and paint wings and horizontal stabilizer\nfrom spar to spar.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>2.3\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Sand and paint door surrounds.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>2.4\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Sand and paint wheel wells.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.25in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>2.5\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Any composite repairs will be accomplished on a time and\nmaterial basis.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.25in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>2.6\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Aircraft\nstripping is considered to be a single application of stripper to remove paint.\nAdditional coats of stripper as required will be billed accordingly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>2.7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 The\nfinal appearance of completed exterior decorative paint surfaces shall meet the\nfollowing requirements when examined at 90- degrees from the painted surface\nand from the distance of 10 feet or more.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>\u00b7</span><span\nstyle='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Exterior daylight examinations are limited to color match, skin\nquality polishing, and other workmanship defects not detected with artificial\nlight sources.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.5in'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>\u00b7</span><span\nstyle='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>The film shall be uniform in appearance and relatively free from\nsags, lint dirt, craters, orange peel, over spray, hazing and pigment float. In\nthe case of rework within a color, it is acceptable to have a slight color\nvariation if the rework does not detract from the overall appearance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>\u00b7</span><span\nstyle='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>High solids nonmetallic \u201cmetallics\u201d have an increased tendency to\norange peel. This increased orange peel is inherent to the materials and shall\nnot be a cause for rejection.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>\u00b7</span><span\nstyle='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>All surface defects will be addressed and corrected prior to\naircraft departure.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in'><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>2.8\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 TIMCO can provide certified, unbranded spot market Jet A\nfuel, upon request at TIMCO\u2019s price plus 10% handling and storage fee, plus an\nupload fee of $.30 per gallon.\u00a0 If upload or download is required for\nperformance of services, then customer shall pay fee of $.30 per gallon, but\nnot the handling and storage, for the fuel uploaded and /or downloaded.</span><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:12.0pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><br>\n<br>\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:7.5pt;text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>\n\n<hr size=2 width=\"100%\" align=center>\n\n</span></div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>Start the year off right. <a\nhref=\"http://body.aol.com/fitness/winter-exercise?NCID=aolcmp00300000002489\"\ntarget=\"_blank\"\ntitle=\"http://body.aol.com/fitness/winter-exercise?NCID=aolcmp00300000002489\">Easy\nways to stay in shape</a> in the new year. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":1,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":1,"is_redacted":false}]